        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You utter an arcane word of power that can make the target @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Blinded]{Blinded} upon hearing it. Once targeted, the target is then temporarily immune for 10 minutes. The effect of the spell depends on the target's level.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>11th or Lower</strong> The target is Blinded permanently.</p>\n<p><strong>12th-13th</strong> The target is Blinded for [[/r 1d4 #minutes]]{1d4 minutes}.</p>\n<p><strong>14th or Higher</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Dazzled]{Dazzled} for 1 minute.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The levels at which each outcome applies increase by 2.</p>"
